Name: assign_worker_to_team
Description: Binary variable to assign a worker to a specific team

Name: assign_team_to_project
Description: Binary variable to assign a team to a specific project

Name: select_user_story_for_sprint
Description: Binary variable to include a user story in a sprint backlog

Name: assign_task_to_worker
Description: Binary variable to assign a task to a specific worker

Name: set_user_story_points
Description: Integer variable to define the story points for a user story

Name: set_feature_priority
Description: Integer variable to set the priority level for a feature

Name: set_project_budget
Description: Continuous variable for allocating a budget to a project

Name: set_sprint_duration
Description: Integer variable to define the length of a sprint in days

Name: allocate_task_effort
Description: Continuous variable to allocate effort (in hours) to a task

Name: select_scrum_master_for_team
Description: Binary variable to assign a scrum master to a team

Name: include_feature_in_release
Description: Binary variable to include a feature in a specific release plan

Name: resolve_blocker
Description: Binary variable that is 1 if a blocker is resolved
